 * at which the source map was found.  This URL is used to compute the
 * sources array.
 *
 * [0]: https://docs.google.com/document/d/1U1RGAehQwRypUTovF1KRlpiOFze0b-_2gc6fAH0KY0k/edit#heading=h.535es3xeprgt
